claim.claim-text:
1. A shotgun shell, comprising:
a casing containing at least wadding, a charge and a primer;
a plurality of shell shot within the casing, wherein the shell shot have a density of at least 10.5 g/cc and are at least substantially formed from an alloy comprising:
tungsten, wherein tungsten forms a majority component of the alloy;
nickel; and
iron, wherein the alloy includes at least 5 wt % nickel and at least 10 wt % iron.
